I would highly recommend this place and will be back.

Had dinner at Fresh Mint last night.
We ordered a delicious green salad, eggplant curry & pad thai.
The salad had a very light and flavorful citrus dressing, walnuts, cranberries, apples, etc...
I wish the portion was a little larger for $9, but it was very tasty.
The pad thai had nice fresh veggies and was very good, but the curry was much better.
It was a little spicy, which I like, and was very flavorful.
It wasn't a coconut milk curry (or had very little) so it was a little different from most Thai green curries I've had, but I loved it.
I definitely would go back to Fresh Mint.
