I work in the airpark and have frankly been surprised to see Fresh Mint stay in business.
When they first opened I tried them for lunch a few times and was underwhelmed, mainly with the slow service and somewhat high prices, and remember thinking they wouldn't succeed.
Fast forward to today and I gave them another try and what a delight it was.
